snippet.title: The Weaponographist  - Launch Trailer!!
snippet.description:
Doug McGrave, famous demon hunter for hire. Highest level, bestest gear, ruggedly handsome, and unrepentant jerk.
For refusing to aid one stinking demon-infested town, you are immediately – and deservedly – cursed. Your powers, your wealth, and your weapons…
Poof! Gone.

Out on Steam now!!

http://store.steampowered.com/app/329240/
http://www.puuba.com
